  "detailed_description": "The original Wizard tells the story of the association of mages who want to prevent Impeficus one of the strongest mages from conquering the world, the story begins when 4 mages of the association invade the castle of impeficus.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhat they don't know is that Impeficus has turned their castle into a sea of ​​challenges specially designed for the onslaught of the wizard association.<br />\r\nDuring the attack the mages will encounter more powerful enemies, enemies from their past and even gods.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe Dungeon Crawler challenges players with different ways to overcome challenges, doing alchemy, collecting resources, buying and selling items, all to get stronger and learn new elemental spells.",
  "about_the_game": "The original Wizard tells the story of the association of mages who want to prevent Impeficus one of the strongest mages from conquering the world, the story begins when 4 mages of the association invade the castle of impeficus.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhat they don't know is that Impeficus has turned their castle into a sea of ​​challenges specially designed for the onslaught of the wizard association.<br />\r\nDuring the attack the mages will encounter more powerful enemies, enemies from their past and even gods.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe Dungeon Crawler challenges players with different ways to overcome challenges, doing alchemy, collecting resources, buying and selling items, all to get stronger and learn new elemental spells.",
